/**
 * Impulse map:
 *
 * 0 reserved (no input)
 *
 * 99: loaded
 *
 * 140: moving clone
 * 141: ctf speedrun
 * 142: fixed clone
 * 143: emergency teleport
 * 148: unfairly eliminate
 *
 * TODO:
 * 200 to 209: prev weapon shortcuts
 * 210 to 219: best weapon shortcuts
 * 220 to 229: next weapon shortcuts
 * 230 to 253: individual weapons (up to 24)
 */

